<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sort-n">sort <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /sɔːt/    美 /sɔːrt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-type-kind">1.★ <strong>种类；类型 (type, kind)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll never do <strong>this sort of</strong> thing.
我绝对不会干这种事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Real friendship should be able to stand <strong>all sorts of</strong> tests.
真正的友谊应该能经得起各种各样的考验。</p><footer>2014 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>What sort of</strong> price were you thinking of?
你想出什么价？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="sort-of">sort of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有几分；有点：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Do you know what I mean?
你知道我什么意思吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Sort of.
知道一点儿。</p></div></div>